This is a fizzy back of a length ball, there to be bit to be honest but Livingstone hasn't gotten into the right position for the pull stroke. Livingstone c Abdul Samad b Rashid Khan 4(6)

Commentary Text: Sandeep Sharma to Jaiswal, out Bowled!! Good comeback from Sandeep Sharma, although Jaiswal is unlucky to drag this on. Friendly full toss, so Jaiswal thought he could jump out again and muscle the ball, but moved a bit too leg-side and had to reach out, in the process under-edged the ball onto the base of off stump. Jaiswal b Sandeep Sharma 36(23) [4s-5 6s-1]
